-COORDINATION AND COMMUNICATION WITH EPA PROJECT MANAGERS, TO INCLUDE PHONE CALLS AND MEETINGS; 
-REVIEW OF HISTORICAL DOCUMENTS AND DATA WHICH PROVIDE SUPPORT TO PROPOSED WORK;
